All Implemented Interfaces:
java.util.Iterator<java.lang.String[]>
Direct Known Subclasses:
BasicTokenPOSLemmaIterator
public abstract class TokenPOSLemmaIterator
extends GenericTokenIterator<java.lang.String[]>

This generic abstract class implements the GenericTokenIterator class for iterating over 3-sized String arrays, each containing the token and its corresponding POS and Lemma annotations. It only implements obtainDataFromToken(Annotation, String).

Author:
moreau
